  {
    "hotel_id": "6196",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/ashburn-hotel/hotel/london-gb.html",
    "name": "Ashburn Hotel",
    "detail": "This GEM of a hotel is in a great location near the heart of London. The hotel itself is nice and small, and very quiet. The continental breakfast was very good, and the staff were always very friendly and smiling. The hotel is within walking distance of many iconic landmarks, like Hyde Park, Royal Albert Hall, Buckingham Palace, etc. Only a short walk to the Gloucester Road underground station. Or if you want to see the sights, take a double-decker bus to Westfield Mall, Baker Street, or Victoria Station. Most trips are just a single bus ride there, with stops near the hotel. We couldn't stop saying just how perfect the location was for this hotel. Our room on the fifth floor was very nice and clean, but doesn't have the big windows that you see on their website. It's basically the attic retrofitted into rooms. If you want nice views, ask for rooms on floors 1 to 4. There are also rooms on street level (rooms numbered 6XX), and in the basement (rooms numbered 7XX). We will definitely consider this hotel if we ever return to London.",
