    "detail": "If you love aviation like I do, you will love this hotel.. get a room with a view of the runway! could have stayed in my room all day just watching planes take off and land at Heathrow. But I didn’t pick this hotel just because I wanted to see planes take off and land.. it’s just one of my personal treats. The location is very convenient if you need to be near the airport. You can walk from the hotels second floor, through an indoor walkway directly into T4. The staff were very kind and friendly. Breakfast was awesome. The rooms, despite being right next to Heathrow were very well insulated and you wouldn’t hear a sound from the outside. Overall very happy and would definitely stay here again. ",
